---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Claim Guardians LLC | Maximizes Your Property Insurance Settlement in Florida" 
  description="Insurance companies underpay property damage claims. Claim Guardians forces your insurer to pay your maximum legal entitlement. You pay zero upfront fees."
>
  <!-- 2. Hero Section (Premium 2026 Aesthetic) -->
  <section class="relative bg-[#0A0F1C] overflow-hidden pt-24 pb-32">
    <!-- Dynamic Glowing Gradient Mesh Background -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 inset-x-0 h-[600px] bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-900/50 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute -top-[300px] -right-[200px] w-[800px] h-[800px] rounded-full bg-primary-600/20 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute -bottom-[200px] -left-[200px] w-[600px] h-[600px] rounded-full bg-accent-600/10 blur-[100px] pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10 mt-8">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center md:text-left">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white mb-8 leading-[1.1] tracking-tight drop-shadow-2xl">
          Claim Guardians <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-400 to-blue-200">Maximizes</span> Your Property Insurance Settlement in Florida.
        </h1>
        <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-300 mb-12 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl font-light mx-auto md:mx-0">
          Insurance companies underpay property damage claims. Claim Guardians forces your insurer to pay your maximum legal entitlement. You pay zero upfront fees. We collect our fee only after you receive your check.
        </h2>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center md:justify-start gap-5 mb-14">
          <a href="/free-claim-review" class="group relative inline-flex justify-center items-center px-10 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white bg-accent-600 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-[0_0_40px_-10px_rgba(234,88,12,0.6)] hover:shadow-[0_0_60px_-15px_rgba(234,88,12,0.8)] transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <span class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent -translate-x-[100%] group-hover:animate-[shimmer_1.5s_infinite]"></span>
            <span class="relative">Get a Free Claim Review</span>
          </a>
          <a href="tel:5551234567" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-10 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/20 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 shadow-xl">
            Emergency? Call Us Now
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Trust Indicators (Glassmorphism Pilled) -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start items-center gap-6 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-300">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
            Florida Licensed Adjusters (FAPIA)
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-white/10">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 15h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v6z"/></svg>
            BBB A+ Rating
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg border border-white/10 text-yellow-500">
            ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ <span class="text-slate-300 ml-1">5-Star Reviews</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Decorative bottom wave/fade -->
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 inset-x-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-base-bg to-transparent"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. Quick Solution Grid -->
  <section class="bg-slate-50 border-y border-slate-200 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          Claim Guardians Resolves Every Type of Property Damage.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-600">
          Property owners face complex insurance policies. Our licensed public adjusters simplify the claims process. Select your damage type below.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <a href="/services/water-damage" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">💧</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Water & Leak Damage</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Claim Guardians uncovers hidden moisture and burst pipe damage.</p>
        </a>
        
        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <a href="/services/hurricane-damage" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🌪️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Hurricane & Storm Damage</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Our experts evaluate wind, hail, and severe weather impacts.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <a href="/services/roof-damage" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🏠</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Roof Leak & Damage</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">We prove structural roof failures to stubborn insurers.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Card 4 -->
        <a href="/services/fire-damage" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🔥</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Fire & Smoke Damage</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Our team assesses structural loss and toxic smoke damage.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Card 5 -->
        <a href="/services/mold-claims" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">🦠</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Mold Damage</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Claim Guardians documents toxic mold growth after water exposure.</p>
        </a>

        <!-- Card 6 -->
        <a href="/services/denied-claims" class="group bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm border border-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-blue-200 transition-all">
          <div class="text-4xl mb-4">❌</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Denied & Underpaid Claims</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">We appeal unfair insurance decisions and demand full payment.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. Social Proof -->
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-16 text-center">
        Claim Guardians Delivers Real Financial Results.
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- Testimonial 1 (Premium UI Card) -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-[0_20px_60px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-[0_30px_80px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] transition-all duration-500 relative group overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-green-500 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>

          <div class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-100 pb-8">
            <span class="inline-flex px-4 py-2 bg-slate-50 text-slate-600 text-sm font-bold rounded-full mb-6 border border-slate-200">
              📍 Water Damage in Miami, FL
            </span>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:items-center text-lg gap-2">
                <span class="text-slate-500 font-medium tracking-wide text-sm uppercase">Insurance Initial Offer</span>
                <span class="text-red-500/60 line-through font-bold text-2xl">~$14,500</span>
              </div>
              <div class="h-px w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-slate-100 to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:items-center text-xl gap-4">
                <span class="text-[#111827] font-bold tracking-wide text-sm uppercase">Claim Guardians Settlement</span>
                <span class="text-green-600 font-black text-4xl tracking-tighter drop-shadow-sm">$82,300</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="text-xl font-medium text-[#111827] leading-relaxed italic border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-6 my-6">
            "The insurance company offered pennies for my flooded kitchen. Claim Guardians handled all the stressful calls and secured enough money to fix everything properly."
          </blockquote>
          <footer class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mt-4 pl-6">– Maria S.</footer>
        </div>

        <!-- Testimonial 2 (Premium UI Card) -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-10 shadow-[0_20px_60px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] border border-slate-100 hover:shadow-[0_30px_80px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] transition-all duration-500 relative group overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-green-500 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>

          <div class="mb-8 border-b border-slate-100 pb-8">
            <span class="inline-flex px-4 py-2 bg-slate-50 text-slate-600 text-sm font-bold rounded-full mb-6 border border-slate-200">
              📍 Roof Damage in Fort Myers, FL
            </span>
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:items-center text-lg gap-2">
                <span class="text-slate-500 font-medium tracking-wide text-sm uppercase">Insurance Initial Offer</span>
                <span class="text-red-500/60 font-bold text-2xl">Claim Denied</span>
              </div>
              <div class="h-px w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-slate-100 to-transparent"></div>
              <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:items-center text-xl gap-4">
                <span class="text-[#111827] font-bold tracking-wide text-sm uppercase">Claim Guardians Settlement</span>
                <span class="text-green-600 font-black text-4xl tracking-tighter drop-shadow-sm">$65,000</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <blockquote class="text-xl font-medium text-[#111827] leading-relaxed italic border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-6 my-6">
            "My insurer denied my storm damage claim completely. Claim Guardians found the hidden proof and forced the company to pay for a full roof replacement."
          </blockquote>
          <footer class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mt-4 pl-6">– David L.</footer>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 5. How We Work (Deep Space 2026 Grid) -->
  <section class="relative bg-[#0A0F1C] py-32 overflow-hidden border-y border-slate-800">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/dark-matter.png')] opacity-20"></div>
    <!-- Mesh Glows -->
    <div class="absolute -left-[200px] top-[100px] w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-primary-600/10 blur-[120px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute -right-[100px] bottom-[0] w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-blue-400/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-20 text-center tracking-tight text-white drop-shadow-lg">
        Claim Guardians Manages Your Entire Claim Process.
      </h2>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
        <!-- Step 1 (Glassmorphism Pilled Card) -->
        <div class="group relative bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 hover:border-primary-500/50 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-transparent rounded-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-500 blur-sm pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="text-6xl font-black text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-400 to-blue-900 mb-8 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 origin-left">01</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-5 text-white">Free Property Inspection.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Claim Guardians inspects your property for free. Our state-licensed adjusters document all hidden damages.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="group relative bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 hover:border-primary-500/50 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-transparent rounded-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-500 blur-sm pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="text-6xl font-black text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-400 to-blue-900 mb-8 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 origin-left">02</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-5 text-white">We Handle the Insurance.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed text-lg">
            Our team files your claim paperwork. We negotiate the maximum payout directly with your insurance company.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="group relative bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl p-10 rounded-3xl border border-white/10 hover:border-primary-500/50 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="absolute -inset-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-transparent rounded-3xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity duration-500 blur-sm pointer-events-none"></div>
          <div class="text-6xl font-black text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-400 to-blue-900 mb-8 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-300 origin-left">03</div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-5 text-white">You Get Paid.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 font-light leading-relaxed text-lg">
            You receive your settlement check. Claim Guardians collects a fee only after you get paid.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6. Objection Handling -->
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-16 text-center">
        Claim Guardians Protects You, Not the Insurance Company.
      </h2>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl overflow-hidden border border-slate-200">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
          <!-- Column 1: The Insurer -->
          <div class="p-10 bg-red-50/50 md:border-r border-slate-200 relative">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-900 mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-red-100 text-red-600">✗</span>
              The Insurance Company's Adjuster
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-6">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">⚠️</span>
                <span class="text-slate-700 text-lg font-medium">The insurance corporation pays them.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">⚠️</span>
                <span class="text-slate-700 text-lg font-medium">They protect the insurer's corporate budget.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-red-500 mt-1">⚠️</span>
                <span class="text-slate-700 text-lg font-medium">They use legal jargon to limit your payout.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Column 2: Us -->
          <div class="p-10 bg-blue-600 text-white relative">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 flex items-center gap-3">
              <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-blue-600">✓</span>
              Claim Guardians (Your Public Adjuster)
            </h3>
            <ul class="space-y-6">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-blue-200 mt-1">✨</span>
                <span class="text-lg font-medium">You hire Claim Guardians.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-blue-200 mt-1">🛡️</span>
                <span class="text-lg font-medium">We protect your family and your property.</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <span class="text-blue-200 mt-1">💰</span>
                <span class="text-lg font-medium">We maximize your financial settlement.</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 7. Frequently Asked Questions -->
  <section class="bg-slate-50 border-t border-slate-200 py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-12 text-center">
        Frequently Asked Questions
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <!-- FAQ 1 -->
        <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-xl text-slate-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">
            <span>How much does a public adjuster cost in Florida?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed border-t border-transparent group-open:border-slate-100 group-open:pt-4">
            Claim Guardians charges $0 in upfront fees. Clients pay a contingency fee only after they receive their settlement. Florida state law caps public adjuster fees at 20% for standard claims.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-xl text-slate-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">
            <span>When should I hire a public adjuster?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed border-t border-transparent group-open:border-slate-100 group-open:pt-4">
            Property owners should hire a public adjuster immediately after discovering property damage. However, you can hire Claim Guardians even if the insurance company already denied your claim.
          </div>
        </details>

        <!-- FAQ 3 -->
        <details class="group bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-2xl [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-bold cursor-pointer list-none p-6 text-xl text-slate-900 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">
            <span>What is the difference between an independent adjuster and a public adjuster?</span>
            <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
              <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24"><path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="text-slate-600 px-6 pb-6 text-lg leading-relaxed border-t border-transparent group-open:border-slate-100 group-open:pt-4">
            The insurance company hires an independent adjuster to protect their corporate budget. You hire a public adjuster to maximize your financial payout. Claim Guardians represents the policyholder exclusively.
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
